name: Into The Void (itch) (MossyBackedSnail, GlitterDemon256)
description:
After an accident at a top secret government lab, you must navigate the void and escape. Before it's too late.

Controls:

A-D = Left/Right   Space = Jump

Known Bugs: Unlocked state of Double Jump Ability isn’t saved.  Disabling abilities aren’t shown in the UI right after unlocking.

Created by MossybackedSnail, Glitterdemon, notjustarat, and Alfa3speed
